strings: <se_low>January: It doesn't rain yet! To blame!
<se_low>King of tricks: I am a general, by no means a demon! Look for crazy pigs!
<se_high>Accuracy: do not worry. We have to find a way to escape from this jail.
<voice_0x01000BDD><se_def>China: Then take control of your emotions. I must first apologize. Can I take that as a comparison?
<voice_0x01000BDF><se_def>China: The upstairs guard overheard our conversation. I'll let you know later. here we go again
